This documentation describes the <%= vars.product_name %>.
<%= vars.product_short %> enables operators to more easily manage large numbers of service instances.


## <a id="overview"></a>Overview

<%= vars.product_short %> gathers information about service instances from multiple
<%= vars.platform_name %> deployments
through the CF API and presents this information in a web UI.
From here, operators can view, filter, and delete service instances.


## <a id="features"></a>Key Features

Through <%= vars.product_short %>, operators can:

* View and filter service instances by foundation, org, space, service offering, status,
  service keys, service bindings, and bound apps
* Delete service instances


