## <a id="reqs"></a>Requirements

<%= vars.product_short %> has the following requirements:

* <%= vars.platform_name %> (formerly <%= vars.platform_old %>) or open source Cloud Foundry
* [User Account and Authentication (UAA) server](https://docs.pivotal.io/pivotalcf/uaa/uaa-overview.html)

## <a id="limitations"></a>Limitations

<%= vars.product_short %> has been tested with 2000 <%= vars.platform_name %> service instances across two <%= vars.platform_name %>
foundations.
Higher numbers might impact the performance of <%= vars.platform_name %> due to the large number of requests made to the Cloud Controller.

